This is mobile four.

258
00:26:14.280 --> 00:26:17.440
There's a traffic accident
ahead. the tunnel is blocked.

259
00:26:19.200 --> 00:26:22.800
"We need to back up and
turn the convoy around."

260
00:26:29.400 --> 00:26:31.040
Something's off.

261
00:26:49.960 --> 00:26:52.080
"This is mobile five. We're taking fire."

262
00:26:53.200 --> 00:26:55.615
Secure stone. Mobile
one. do you copy me?

263
00:26:55.639 --> 00:26:56.639
Mobile one.

264
00:26:56.920 --> 00:26:59.360
"Mobile five. come in."

265
00:27:08.920 --> 00:27:10.576
Get down!

266
00:27:10.600 --> 00:27:13.360
Aahh!

267
00:27:14.720 --> 00:27:17.840
Aahh!

268
00:27:24.000 --> 00:27:26.039
Move! Go. go. go. go!

269
00:27:42.160 --> 00:27:44.336
Get back-up in there.
There is no back-up.

270
00:27:44.360 --> 00:27:47.136
I mean any police officer in
the vicinity with a fucking gun.

271
00:27:47.160 --> 00:27:48.919
Just move!

272
00:28:02.080 --> 00:28:04.456
Hey! Get me out of here!

273
00:28:04.480 --> 00:28:07.296
Hey!

274
00:28:07.320 --> 00:28:08.839
They're coming for me!

275
00:28:25.040 --> 00:28:27.400
Mobile one. do you have eyes on stone?

276
00:28:34.800 --> 00:28:37.040
Take cover! Move!

277
00:28:52.280 --> 00:28:54.320
Hey! Open the door!

278
00:29:18.120 --> 00:29:19.920
Hey!

279
00:29:26.880 --> 00:29:29.039
Get me out of here!

280
00:29:30.960 --> 00:29:33.320
Let me out! Open the door!

281
00:29:39.640 --> 00:29:41.480
Open the door!

282
00:30:18.160 --> 00:30:19.936
Where the fuck are those police?

283
00:30:19.960 --> 00:30:22.000
Two minutes out. ma'am.

284
00:30:27.640 --> 00:30:29.720
We need to move.

285
00:30:34.160 --> 00:30:37.360
What are you doing? So you can't run.

286
00:30:40.560 --> 00:30:43.040
Fuck!

287
00:30:56.160 --> 00:30:58.160
What are you doing?
Making us disappear.

288
00:31:08.400 --> 00:31:10.560
I need the battery.

289
00:32:20.560 --> 00:32:22.440
Come on. run.

290
00:32:51.040 --> 00:32:53.399
We've gotta get off this road.

291
00:33:01.480 --> 00:33:04.056
Wait. wait. wait. wait.
wait. What're you doing?

292
00:33:04.080 --> 00:33:06.200
Hold your breath when we hit the water.

293
00:33:07.400 --> 00:33:08.856
Are you out of your fucking mind?

294
00:33:08.880 --> 00:33:11.256
We'll be pulled under briefly.

295
00:33:11.280 --> 00:33:14.736
Just float for a second. get
your bearings. and swim with me.

296
00:33:14.760 --> 00:33:16.840
No way! No fucking way!

297
00:33:28.320 --> 00:33:32.056
She's coming to get
us. It's the only way out.

298
00:33:32.080 --> 00:33:33.192
Do you want to die here. Amber?

299
00:33:33.216 --> 00:33:34.456
- Of course I don't.
- Then we jump.

300
00:33:34.480 --> 00:33:37.296
I... come on. No. Please.

301
00:33:37.320 --> 00:33:38.896
Quick!

302
00:33:38.920 --> 00:33:41.160
My god. ok. Quick!

303
00:33:53.600 --> 00:33:55.560
Hoo!

304
00:33:59.680 --> 00:34:02.880
Ready? Wait. Just wait. Wait.

305
00:34:20.440 --> 00:34:22.680
How we looking? Everything golden?

306
00:34:28.120 --> 00:34:30.360
I don't have him yet.

307
00:34:31.400 --> 00:34:33.840
Shit. Fuck!

308
00:34:48.323 --> 00:34:50.640
"Eight armed police officers are dead."

309
00:34:51.680 --> 00:34:53.496
"Two ncu protection detail."

310
00:34:53.520 --> 00:34:55.856
"Here's one body in the burnt-out truck:."

311
00:34:55.880 --> 00:34:58.136
"A male prison transportation officer."

312
00:34:58.160 --> 00:35:00.576
Any sign of the prisoner?
"Negative. ma'am. He's missing."

313
00:35:00.600 --> 00:35:02.935
"So is the second transport officer."

314
00:35:02.959 --> 00:35:05.479
- Maybe they got away with him.
- Somehow. - Get me their file.

315
00:35:05.960 --> 00:35:08.536
O'Neill. I need to know if there
was any chatter around this hit.

316
00:35:08.560 --> 00:35:10.096
Names. Exit packages. Anything.

317
00:35:10.120 --> 00:35:12.736
On it. Throw a perimeter
around the area.

318
00:35:12.760 --> 00:35:14.296
with every available officer.

319
00:35:14.320 --> 00:35:17.000
The prison transport officer's
details are incoming. ma'am.

320
00:35:18.240 --> 00:35:20.376
Amber Todd. Three years in post.

321
00:35:20.400 --> 00:35:22.336
She completed basic
control and restraint

322
00:35:22.360 --> 00:35:24.536
and de-escalation training.
no firearms experience.

323
00:35:24.560 --> 00:35:27.056
or advanced scenario-based drills.

324
00:35:27.080 --> 00:35:30.296
Then she's out of her
depth even if she is still alive.

325
00:35:30.320 --> 00:35:32.400
I need to speak with you alone.

326
00:35:46.320 --> 00:35:48.096
I'm sorry. Jo.

327
00:35:48.120 --> 00:35:50.680
Every step of the way I've been
assuring people you've got this.

328
00:35:51.520 --> 00:35:54.936
And look at the state of
you. I won't let you down.

329
00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:56.816
It's too late. Alex.

330
00:35:56.840 --> 00:35:59.456
Jesus. seven fucking
years. And for what?

331
00:35:59.480 --> 00:36:01.936
11 people just died in that tunnel.

332
00:36:01.960 --> 00:36:04.136
And our key witness is gone.

333
00:36:04.160 --> 00:36:06.256
What the hell were you thinking?

334
00:36:06.280 --> 00:36:08.696
You should have got clearance
from me to move stone.

335
00:36:08.720 --> 00:36:10.656
There wasn't enough time. If he dies

336
00:36:10.680 --> 00:36:12.576
and the case against dempsey collapses.

337
00:36:12.600 --> 00:36:14.520
I'll hold you responsible.

338
00:36:18.280 --> 00:36:19.960
Now. find him.

339
00:36:56.000 --> 00:36:58.279
What the fuck just happened?

340
00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:04.440
Come on.

341
00:37:06.440 --> 00:37:08.496
She'll be tracking us. Who is she?

342
00:37:08.520 --> 00:37:10.176
I trained her.

343
00:37:10.200 --> 00:37:13.136
We have to call your
people to get us out of here.

344
00:37:13.160 --> 00:37:15.000
Ok.

345
00:37:16.040 --> 00:37:17.880
There.

346
00:37:23.240 --> 00:37:25.720
It's alright! Bless you. bless you.

347
00:37:29.000 --> 00:37:31.079
Do you wanna see a bit of TV?

348
00:37:32.880 --> 00:37:34.839
It's alright.

349
00:37:39.120 --> 00:37:41.376
"The convoy was ambushed
in what officials are calling"

350
00:37:41.400 --> 00:37:45.256
"a calculated militarised
assault that left 11 people dead."

351
00:37:45.280 --> 00:37:48.856
"Including eight police officers.
two national crime units' agents"

352
00:37:48.880 --> 00:37:51.439
"and one prison transport officer."

353
00:37:55.560 --> 00:37:57.280
Come on.

354
00:37:59.040 --> 00:38:01.576
Pick up. Pick up.

355
00:38:01.600 --> 00:38:03.776
"This is Amber. I can't
get to the phone right now."

356
00:38:03.800 --> 00:38:06.000
"but I'm all yours after the beep!"

357
00:38:22.120 --> 00:38:24.216
Ok. there's no phone.

358
00:38:24.240 --> 00:38:26.296
We have to keep moving.
If she's tracking us.

359
00:38:26.320 --> 00:38:28.896
we can't stand still. What the fuck?

360
00:38:28.920 --> 00:38:30.856
What are you doing?

361
00:38:30.880 --> 00:38:32.816
You have to stop the bleeding.

362
00:38:32.840 --> 00:38:34.896
What bleeding? My back.

363
00:38:34.920 --> 00:38:37.656
Fuck. Pull out the shrapnel

364
00:38:37.680 --> 00:38:40.656
and clean the wound.
If I lose consciousness.

365
00:38:40.680 --> 00:38:43.376
I could go into a diabetic coma. Ok.

366
00:38:43.400 --> 00:38:45.640
Ok. I can do that.

367
00:38:52.720 --> 00:38:55.520
I can't reach it. So. unlock us.

368
00:39:01.240 --> 00:39:03.376
Er. I lost them when we jumped. Fuck.

369
00:39:03.400 --> 00:39:05.055
Find something to smash them with.

370
00:39:05.079 --> 00:39:06.919
These are reinforced
alloy. I need a blowtorch

371
00:39:07.040 --> 00:39:10.200
to even make a dent. Ok?
You're going to have to help me.

372
00:39:17.000 --> 00:39:18.920
Ok.

373
00:39:22.240 --> 00:39:24.056
Fuck. Pull it out.

374
00:39:24.080 --> 00:39:27.936
With what? With your
fucking hands. Just do it!

375
00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:29.176
Here for the pain.

376
00:39:29.200 --> 00:39:32.720
I don't need that. Do it.

377
00:39:34.400 --> 00:39:36.016
Ok.

378
00:39:36.040 --> 00:39:38.496
Wait. Wait. Wait.

379
00:39:38.520 --> 00:39:41.120
Give me the fucking ruler.

380
00:39:51.080 --> 00:39:53.080
Ok. I'm gonna pull now.

381
00:39:54.640 --> 00:39:56.536
Alright.

382
00:40:16.120 --> 00:40:19.176
Ok. Give me your
hand. Give me your hand.

383
00:40:19.200 --> 00:40:22.760
Clean the wound and bandage it.

384
00:40:31.200 --> 00:40:32.736
You could have run.

385
00:40:32.760 --> 00:40:34.936
Ready? Alcohol.

386
00:40:45.360 --> 00:40:47.536
Why did you come back for me?

387
00:40:47.560 --> 00:40:49.400
It's my job to get you to court.

388
00:40:52.160 --> 00:40:54.400
Who are you?

389
00:40:55.680 --> 00:40:57.816
Who are these people trying to kill you?

390
00:40:57.840 --> 00:41:00.000
My name is tibor stone.

391
00:41:00.880 --> 00:41:05.336
I'm a material witness against
an organisation called Pegasus.

392
00:41:05.360 --> 00:41:07.320
My former employers.

393
00:41:09.200 --> 00:41:11.000
I'm testifying on Friday.

394
00:41:13.560 --> 00:41:15.560
Unless they get to me first.

395
00:41:20.480 --> 00:41:22.536
And the woman who's hunting you...

396
00:41:22.560 --> 00:41:24.456
You said that you trained her.

397
00:41:24.480 --> 00:41:27.000
You trained her to do what?

398
00:41:29.480 --> 00:41:31.039
To kill people.

399
00:41:37.240 --> 00:41:40.216
What the bloody hell
are you doing in here?

400
00:41:40.240 --> 00:41:43.896
It's ok. It's ok. I'm a
prison transport officer.

401
00:41:43.920 --> 00:41:46.800
Ok. I need to use your phone.
please sir. It's an emergency.

402
00:41:48.000 --> 00:41:50.280
Sir. It's Amber Todd.

403
00:41:57.200 --> 00:41:58.536
Todd?

404
00:41:58.560 --> 00:42:00.816
This is ncu operations director tebbit.

405
00:42:00.840 --> 00:42:02.696
Is stone with you? "Yes. sir."

406
00:42:02.720 --> 00:42:04.376
Thank Christ.

407
00:42:04.400 --> 00:42:07.360
"Are you ok?" I'm fine. But Joe...

408
00:42:09.880 --> 00:42:12.216
My partner is dead.

409
00:42:12.240 --> 00:42:14.336
I-I'm sorry to hear that.

410
00:42:14.360 --> 00:42:16.640
And what... what condition is stone in?

411
00:42:17.640 --> 00:42:20.616
He... he has a wound to his
back. but he's... he's stable.

412
00:42:20.640 --> 00:42:22.536
Right. what's your location.

413
00:42:22.560 --> 00:42:24.616
We'll get an evac team
to you and get you out.

414
00:42:24.640 --> 00:42:27.535
"Er. we're... we're in a river guard hut."

415
00:42:27.559 --> 00:42:28.719
"The docks on the east side."

416
00:42:29.480 --> 00:42:32.376
Half a mile downstream from the
tunnel. "Right. We're on our way."

417
00:42:32.400 --> 00:42:35.320
Ok. And. Todd...

418
00:42:36.320 --> 00:42:38.256
You watch yourself with stone.

419
00:42:38.280 --> 00:42:40.760
"He worked as a contract
killer for Pegasus."

420
00:42:42.960 --> 00:42:44.496
47 confirmed kills.

421
00:42:44.520 --> 00:42:46.960
and that's only the ones we know about.

422
00:42:52.440 --> 00:42:54.359
Good luck.

423
00:42:58.560 --> 00:43:00.120
Shit. Help me. please!

424
00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:02.336
Help me!

425
00:43:02.360 --> 00:43:05.360
Tibor? Tibor.

426
00:43:07.680 --> 00:43:10.880
How far away are they? Any second. sir.

427
00:43:19.160 --> 00:43:21.160
Not Insulin.

428
00:43:22.120 --> 00:43:24.440
I need a glucagon shot.

429
00:43:25.480 --> 00:43:28.840
This one? Yeah.

430
00:43:58.920 --> 00:44:02.336
It's ok. I'll go and get them.

431
00:44:02.360 --> 00:44:04.359
Ok.

432
00:45:25.920 --> 00:45:28.519
Hello. Nina.

